---
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>SABM | The Scientific Collection</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;1,700&family=Inter:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        .pedestal-border { border: 0.5px solid #D4AF37; }
        .lithograph-filter { filter: contrast(1.1) sepia(0.1); }
