            <h2 class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.5em] text-stone-400 mb-8 italic">The Collection</h2>
            <p class="font-['Playfair_Display'] text-5xl leading-tight">
                A definitive archive of <span class="italic">Southern African</span> flora, preserved for global science and sovereign trade.
            </p>
        </header>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-24">
            
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
                <div class="pedestal-border w-full aspect-[4/5] flex items-center justify-center p-12 bg-[#fcfcfc] hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-stone-200 transition-all duration-700 ease-in-out group">
                    <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/30/Sceletium_tortuosum_botanical.jpg/800px-Sceletium_tortuosum_botanical.jpg" 
                         alt="Sceletium Illustration" 
                         class="lithograph-filter group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-1000" />
                </div>
